# 🇨🇳 **FUNDING RATES & LIQUIDITY IN CHINA MACRO TRADING**

### (DR007, SHIBOR, OMO, RRR, MLF, Window Guidance — and how they interact)

![Image](https://s3.tradingview.com/w/wb5kFP4E_mid.webp?v=1677199718\&utm_source=chatgpt.com)

![Image](https://cdn.macromicro.me/files/charts/935/935-en.png?v=1755117749\&utm_source=chatgpt.com)

